__ Cantrip: Protection from Cantrips __________ Cost: 25 _____________________

Use: cantrip protect                            Material Component: none
Use: C protect

The cantrip protection from cantrips is a minor magic of the sphere of 
abjuration.  When traced, the rune of protection from cantrips covers
the bard with an invisible shield, protecting them from the effects of
all cantrips.  While this spell is in effect, the caster may not cast
any cantrips.  An absolute must have spell for any tutor of low level 
bards! 
